<Topic
  title="Audit log and compliance — what's recorded, what's queryable, what an auditor wants"
  description="If a compliance auditor asks 'who renewed cert X on date Y and from what IP', CertMate answers in one query. Here's the schema, what's captured, what isn't, and how to wire the audit log into the rest of your SIEM."
  slug="audit-and-compliance"
  readTime="6 min"
